---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="bg-slate-950 text-slate-400 mt-24">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-8">
      <div>
        <p class="font-bold text-white text-lg mb-2">
          mike<span class="text-sky-500">tone</span>
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed">
          音声作品シナリオ制作・<br />サークル運営補助・確定申告補助
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="text-white font-semibold text-sm mb-3">ページ</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li><a href="/services" class="hover:text-sky-400 transition-colors">サービス</a></li>
          <li><a href="/portfolio" class="hover:text-sky-400 transition-colors">ポートフォリオ</a></li>
          <li><a href="/blog" class="hover:text-sky-400 transition-colors">ブログ</a></li>
          <li><a href="/contact" class="hover:text-sky-400 transition-colors">お問い合わせ</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="text-white font-semibold text-sm mb-3">お問い合わせ</p>
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-sky-500 hover:bg-sky-600 text-white text-sm font-semibold rounded-lg transition-colors"
        >
          依頼・相談はこちら
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="border-t border-slate-800 pt-6 text-xs text-center">
      &copy; {year} miketone. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
